{"tid":1133560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葵涌男住客租務糾紛激動危坐窗邊 兩警合力救回一命","createTime":"2019-05-01T07:03:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T07:04:50.000Z","uid":3090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"07a0ab226893a3056c72449c28e480cbc79330cd","tid":1133560,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T07:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MsYvRf1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMsYvRf1.png&h=b5e42eb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男住客因租務問題激動危坐窗邊，警員到場勸解拉回安全位置。劉柏麟攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/siVBMPt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsiVBMPt.png&h=5b25f720&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉柏麟攝<br />\n<br />\n葵涌青山公路482號和記新邨，中午近12時半，年約60歲男住客與業主因租務糾紛發生爭執，男住客激動危坐窗邊，兩男女警員接報到場勸解，合力將男事主拉回屋內，其中男警及男住客輕微擦傷，兩人均拒絕送院，警方經調查後列糾紛事件處理。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEC8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=e529ae2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"cf8b798eafaf328c3820090381718fb4226f51c5","tid":1133560,"uid":36296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T07:04:50.000Z","msg":"業主心諗：好撚彩姐 如果唔見幾百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}